                           We're here to help you!
    EMPLOYMENT OPPORTUNITIES within the Office of Real Estate Appraisers:
         OREA Employment Listings are available from the State Personnel
                                  Board website

       OREA also has several open exams currently listed on the State
              Personnel Board website, for the following positions:

     * Property Appraiser/Investigator
     * Senior Property Appraiser/Investigator
     * Supervising Property Appraiser/Investigator

                 CONTRACTING AND PROCUREMENT OPPORTUNITIES:
     OREA has a new page for Contracting and Procurement Opportunities.



